Class ChildrenStream$<TDomain>

ChildrenStream$

Base class used to define advanced children policy in VirtualDOM when the source stream emit array of domain data.

You can derive you own class by providing the implementation of update.

Example of use: AppendOnlyPolicy, ReplacePolicy.
